{"tid":1733254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣軍師上線喇","createTime":"2019-11-18T05:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:47:00.000Z","uid":175542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6595f3dd18749a449ef4241f4d9ff5a69dbe9b","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，為左係poly入面講左幾日都唔走又屌人散水狗既前線，我地已經失去左更多支援既手足，琴晚仲打左成晚仗，事後檢討唔而家做，而家諗下有咩對策<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好再零星既手足去戈到幫拖，送頭架咋<br />\n2. 識有人係入面經火車軌出黎但黃左，所以叫傳媒唔好影出口<br />\n3. 要空中運energy bar 入去，少量運幾次，運完就走，唔好諗著揸番出黎<br />\n4. 大量文宣煲大佢（人道立場，外國支援），可以放棄藍絲立場，聽撚住佢地講全部殺曬就岩<br />\n5. 同時要遊擊警宿同藍店，唔好搞中聯辦喇（要搞就遊擊，以快打慢，因為一定重兵）<br />\n6. 同入面手足要有緊密聯絡，唔好比佢地心理崩潰<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾多，集思廣益"},{"pid":"d2a728414fbe7d0bb2ce1ede9a81e18f61cdea32","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"推0/10"},{"pid":"a3eafbd9c6186d8ee799038832433c13d6457aab","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"7c96fd036bac89eb7a4a57ff4b8591e286eadc4e","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"2fa3ed1f5534a25b5e6074ce77de613aa729adc4","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"2b547a468edb6e59bb5bfb8bfcdb19c9b1450b08","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"3ee0056bd148618dfbf240c00e953c6b8cf66015","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"fd46c51c6494dcd38090407d08b3e829f32e86bd","tid":1733254,"uid":175542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"4aecb743fe13fa1f5d05651d83c75e3e10dc531f","tid":1733254,"uid"